model.name: Friday Night Funkin Pack
model.description: A Friday Night Funkin model and map pack for Beat Saber! This model pack contains: custom notes, sabers, and 7 custom environments. Additionally, all 22 songs from the OST have been included in a seperate playlist file. All maps have easy, hard, and expert+ so everybody can play! PC version can be found [here](https://bobbie.dev/FNFPack). If you like this pack consider joining my [patreon](https://www.patreon.com/bobbievr)!
